        <mxCell id="vlQklLCOxlCWhmk4wWh2-23" value="This notebook imports the IPCC_report.txt and performs the following:&lt;div&gt;1. counts total: 6135 DOIs&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. removes resolvers: 4675 had https://doi.org/ or http://doi.org/ or 33.9% of total&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.remove duplicate DOIs - 231 DOIs were used 2 or more times, removed 253 DOIs, 5883 DOIs are unique&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. check for registration status: as of April 10, 5845 registered with Crossref, 29 not registered, 7 with DataCite, 2 with ISTIC&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. saved out as &quot;IPCC_Reposrt_cleaned_DOIs.txt&quot;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
