        <mxCell id="vlQklLCOxlCWhmk4wWh2-34" value="DOI_search.ipynb" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="50" y="760" width="120" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vlQklLCOxlCWhmk4wWh2-36" value="This notebook looks for titles using the OpenAlex REST API search:&lt;div&gt;1. Extract titles between first &quot;: &quot; and next &quot;. &quot; keeping what is between. this should be the title&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. lower() and replace punctuation with space&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. title is sent to API call:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; white-space: pre; color: rgb(206, 145, 120);&quot;&gt;https://api.openalex.org/works?filter=title.search:&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; white-space: pre; color: rgb(86, 156, 214);&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; white-space: pre; color: rgb(86, 156, 214);&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; white-space: pre; color: rgb(206, 145, 120);&quot;&gt;&quot;&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. retrieves oa_id, and oa_title, and results count&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; white-space: pre; color: rgb(206, 145, 120);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. saved out as two files: one where the match was 1 and another where result was more than 1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;5.1: 112 had a match of just 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;5.2 150 had a match of more than 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. calculated Levenshtein seqratio distance but this was of little use&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7. saved as &#39;merged_df_ones.txt&#39; and &#39;merged_df_morethans.txt&#39;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="190" y="795" width="660" height="75" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
